message: digbaz ershad 10th election a ongso nibena bolese,amar mone hoy ata awami sorjontro,kivabe boli,"awami election comission notun kore tofsil ghosona korar jonno ershad ke podotager moto sajano natok korese"karon take podotag na korale andoloner nikot bossata sikar kore ponray tafsil tader pestige lage,tara to pastige rokkha korte poro banglar jonogonke guli kore merfele dite pare.mamun
